<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/386470-i-didn-t-like-the-way-of-shadows-because-i">I didn&#39;t like The Way of Shadows because I felt the writing was immature and the plot badly developed. Do you think that I will like this book? Does Weeks show improvement between this series and the Night Angel Trilogy?</a>
</div>
