<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The knife used by Kip and only a few others was called the Blinding Knife. My theory on this is because it grows along with it&apos;s owner&apos;s abilities (Ki<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The knife used by Kip and only a few others was called the Blinding Knife. My theory on this is because it grows along with it's owner's abilities (Kip's abilities) and that it is called the Blinding Knife also because it takes away the colours that the person who was stabbed can draft while transfering them to the blade.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
